At the start of your Draw Phase, if your Life Points are lower than your opponent's and this card is in your Graveyard because it was destroyed by your opponent's card (either by battle or by card effect) and sent there since your last Draw Phase: You can shout "I'm feeling the flow!"; choose 1 card from your Deck and place it on top of your Deck.
